OL,3,C#1.6m in cash found hidden at drug
OL,4,Cdealer's house
OL,6,FMore than #1.6 million was found
OL,7,Fstashed in secret compartments at a
OL,8,Fdrug dealer's house in the biggest
OL,9,Fever single cash seizure by West
OL,10,FYorkshire Police.
OL,12,FOfficers initially found #230,000
OL,13,Falong with heroin and ketamine when
OL,14,Fthey raided Zulfiqar Shah's home in
OL,15,FRhylstone Mount, Bradford, on 7 August
OL,16,Flast year.
OL,18,FShah, 58, and his partner Joanne
OL,19,FLeriche were both charged with drugs
OL,20,Foffences and remanded in custody.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
