FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778415071
OL,3,C#1.6m in cash found hidden at drug
OL,4,Cdealer's house
OL,6,FFurther intelligence suggested there
OL,7,Fwas more cash hidden at the property
OL,8,Fand officers carried out another
OL,9,Fsearch in October.
OL,11,FThey found hidden compartments built
OL,12,Finto two bedroom wardrobes, containing
OL,13,Fabout #1.4m.
OL,15,FShah, admitted conspiracy to supply
OL,16,Fheroin and ketamine and conspiracy to
OL,17,Fpossess criminal property at Bradford
OL,18,FCrown Court.
OL,20,FHe was jailed for 16 years and six
OL,21,Fmonths.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
