CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778415071
OL,3,C#1.6m in cash found hidden at drug
OL,4,Cdealer's house
OL,6,FLeriche, 51, had already been jailed
OL,7,Ffor 13 months after pleading guilty to
OL,8,Ftwo counts of allowing a premises to
OL,9,Fbe used for drug dealing.
OL,11,FDet Insp Chris Rukin, who led the
OL,12,Finvestigation, said: "Shah was someone
OL,13,Fheavily involved in the supply of
OL,14,Fclass A drugs and the huge amount of
OL,15,Fmoney he was found with clearly
OL,16,Fillustrates the scale of his
OL,17,Finvolvement.
