OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778415071
OL,3,C#1.6m in cash found hidden at drug
OL,4,Cdealer's house
OL,6,F"This is the biggest single seizure of
OL,7,Fcriminal cash in West Yorkshire and
OL,8,Fbehind all that money lies the
OL,9,Fsignificant negative impact of the
OL,10,Fsupply of illegal drugs, which fuels
OL,11,Fcrime and serious violence in our
OL,12,Fcommunities and brings misery to the
OL,13,Flives of individual users and their
OL,14,Ffamilies."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
